# Sampul Journey Template

Use this template when building any multi-step journey in Sampul.

## Journey Structure (5 Steps)

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│ INTRO → SELECTION → DETAILS → REVIEW → SUCCESS → DASHBOARD │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

## Page 1: Intro Screen

### Required Elements
```dart
Column(
  children: [
    // 1. Clear headline (non-intimidating)
    Text("Organise your [items]"),
    
    // 2. Short subtext (context)
    Text("Include your [items] so your instructions are clear..."),
    
    // 3. Definition block (clarity)
    DefinitionCard(
      title: "[Items] may include:",
      items: ["Item type 1", "Item type 2", "Item type 3"],
    ),
    
    // 4. Benefits block (outcome-based)
    BenefitsCard(
      title: "Why this matters:",
      items: ["Prevent X from being lost", "Ensure proper Y"],
    ),
    
    // 5. Security reassurance
    SecurityNote("We do not store [sensitive data]."),
    
    // 6. Single CTA
    PrimaryButton("Add [item]"),
  ],
)
```

### Checklist
- [ ] Headline is action-oriented, non-scary
- [ ] Definition block clarifies scope
- [ ] Benefits are consequence-based
- [ ] Security reassurance present
- [ ] Single primary CTA

---

## Page 2: Selection Screen

### Required Elements
```dart
Column(
  children: [
    // 1. Clear header
    Text("Select a [item type]"),
    
    // 2. Search bar (instant filter)
    SearchBar(
      hint: "Search for a [item] or [category]",
      onChanged: (query) => filterResults(query),
    ),
    
    // 3. Category tabs (reduce scroll)
    CategoryTabs([
      Tab("Popular"),
      Tab("Category 1"),
      Tab("Category 2"),
    ]),
    
    // 4. Popular items grid (6-8 items)
    PopularGrid(items: popularItems),
    
    // 5. Custom option
    CustomOptionLink("Can't find your [item]? Add custom"),
    
    // 6. Footer note
    FooterNote("You'll provide instructions in the next step."),
  ],
)
```

### Checklist
- [ ] Search filters instantly (no submit)
- [ ] Categories reduce cognitive load
- [ ] Popular items have visual icons
- [ ] Custom option is visible
- [ ] No details collected here (selection only)

---

## Page 3: Details Screen

### Required Elements
```dart
Column(
  children: [
    // 1. Selection confirmation
    SelectionHeader(
      item: selectedItem,
      onChangePressed: () => navigateBack(),
    ),
    
    // 2. Section A: Optional fields
    OptionalSection(
      label: "Estimated value (optional)",
      child: TextField(),
    ),
    
    // 3. Section B: Structured choices
    InstructionSection(
      label: "What should happen to this [item]?",
      options: [
        Option("Close this [item]"),
        Option("Transfer access to my executor"),
        Option("Leave specific instructions"),
      ],
    ),
    
    // 4. Section C: Additional notes (optional)
    OptionalSection(
      label: "Additional notes (optional)",
      child: TextField(maxLines: 3),
    ),
    
    // 5. Security reassurance with icon
    SecurityNoteWithIcon(
      "We do not store [sensitive data]. "
      "This information will only be accessible "
      "according to your estate instructions."
    ),
    
    // 6. CTA
    PrimaryButton("Save [item]"),
  ],
)
```

### Checklist
- [ ] Selection confirmed at top
- [ ] Structured options (not open text)
- [ ] Optional fields clearly marked
- [ ] Security reassurance with shield icon
- [ ] Single primary CTA

---

## Page 4: Review Screen

### Required Elements
```dart
Column(
  children: [
    // 1. Header
    Text("Review this [item]"),
    
    // 2. Summary card
    SummaryCard(
      rows: [
        SummaryRow("Label", value, onEdit: () {}),
        SummaryRow("Label", value, onEdit: () {}),
      ],
    ),
    
    // 3. Short security reminder (one line)
    SecurityNote("[Sensitive data] is not stored in Sampul."),
    
    // 4. CTAs
    Row(
      children: [
        SecondaryButton("Back"),
        PrimaryButton("Save [item]"),
      ],
    ),
  ],
)
```

### Checklist
- [ ] Card-based summary (clean)
- [ ] Each row has edit option
- [ ] Security reminder is short
- [ ] NOT a legal review screen
- [ ] Two CTAs only (Back + Save)

---

## Page 5: Success Screen

### Required Elements
```dart
Column(
  children: [
    // 1. Status indicator
    SuccessIcon(), // Checkmark, no confetti
    Text("✓ [Item] added"),
    
    // 2. Reinforcement line
    Text("Your instruction has been recorded securely."),
    
    // 3. Primary CTA
    PrimaryButton("Return to dashboard"),
    
    // 4. Subtle secondary
    TextButton("Add another [item]"),
  ],
)
```

### Checklist
- [ ] No celebration/confetti
- [ ] Professional confirmation
- [ ] Short reinforcement line
- [ ] Clear primary CTA
- [ ] Subtle secondary option

---

## Animation Guidelines

### Allowed
- Subtle checkmark fade-in
- Smooth transitions between screens
- Progress indicator updates

### Not Allowed
- Confetti
- Bounce effects
- Sound effects
- Flash animations
- Particle effects

